HEADWORD: witching
<hw>witch"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>That witches or enchants; suited
to enchantment or witchcraft; bewitching.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧The very
<xex>witching</xex> time of night.⟦rdquo⟧ <au>Shak.</au> --
<wordforms><wf>Witch"ing*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
